content:
Oh, it'll be 1 more day until I discover a new sleeping spot{打哈欠}...
Until then...
I think I'll just rest here for a bit...{打哈欠}

Huff... huff...{短暂停}
Like this—loading myself up with,
Overflowing energy!

*huff* *huff*—{打瞌睡}
Did I fall asleep just now?
Heh, that's so like me.

Gahaha~ha!
It's for dress-up! {短暂停}
I occasionally do magical performances like this too.

Hey there, traveler!
I just woke up. {打哈欠}
Oh, it's already Tuesday.

Oh visitor~ dear visitor!~ DEAR VISITOR!!!
A delightful performance is about to begin! <color=#d3b037>{Pnickname}</color>,
I'm practicing my Saturday lines right now! {想象中}

It all feels like such a distant memory...
In my mind, I only have memories of living together with everyone...
Could it be that I've never actually been to the amusement park? {想象中}
